539
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,400
You hit my wife.

540
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:39,640
You're asking for a beating.

541
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,360
My husband saw that I was beaten,

542
00:24:44,600 --> 00:24:45,600
