545
00:24:49,840 --> 00:24:50,840
In desperation,

546
00:24:51,520 --> 00:24:51,840
I found

547
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:53,160
the rope I had already prepared

548
00:24:53,520 --> 00:24:54,760
and rushed up to

549
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:56,160
