566
00:25:38,520 --> 00:25:40,120
Dacheng. What did he say?

567
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:44,720
Xue Juanhong.

568
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:47,040
All you have to do now is

569
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:48,920
