580
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,400
He shouldn't have been involved in this matter.

581
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:10,920
He stopped me from beginning to end.

582
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:14,200
So

583
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:17,720
