587
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:29,200
Xue Juanhong.

588
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,000
Let me remind you.

589
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,960
As your defense lawyer,

590
00:26:33,040 --> 00:26:33,880
